    <item>
      <title>Cross-Planet Logistics -- What to Ship Between Planets and Cargo Rocket Automation</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1319/space-age/cross-planet-logistics/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1319/space-age/cross-planet-logistics/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Cross-planet logistics in Space Age is the biggest leap in complexity from vanilla Factorio. You now manage 5 planets plus space platforms, each with unique resources that only produce on that planet. The challenge is knowing WHAT to ship, WHEN to ship it, and HOW to automate the shipping so you don&#39;t end up with 10,000 calcite and zero holmium plates.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;pro-tip&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TL;DR:&lt;/strong&gt; Every planet exports its unique resource and imports everything else from Nauvis. Build a dedicated cargo rocket landing pad on each planet with circuit-controlled requests. Set rocket launch conditions to fire when the destination drops below 2 hours of usage. Never ship raw ore between planets -- ship plates, circuits, and finished goods.&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;planet-importexport-reference&#34;&gt;Planet Import/Export Reference&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;table&gt;&#xA;  &lt;thead&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Planet&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Exports (send to Nauvis)&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Imports (receive from Nauvis)&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th style=&#34;text-align: center&#34;&gt;Priority&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;  &lt;tbody&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Nauvis&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Everything&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Nothing (hub)&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: center&#34;&gt;--&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Vulcanus&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/foundry.png&#34; alt=&#34;foundry&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Foundry&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;, &lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/calcite.png&#34; alt=&#34;calcite&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Calcite&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;, &lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/molten_iron.png&#34; alt=&#34;molten_iron&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Molten iron&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;/&lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/molten_copper.png&#34; alt=&#34;molten_copper&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Molten&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Uranium fuel cells, &lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/quality_module.png&#34; alt=&#34;quality_module&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Quality&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;s&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: center&#34;&gt;⭐⭐⭐&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Fulgora&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/holmium_plate.png&#34; alt=&#34;holmium_plate&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Holmium&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;, &lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/electromagnetic_plant.png&#34; alt=&#34;electromagnetic_plant&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Electromagne&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;, &lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/superconductor.png&#34; alt=&#34;superconductor&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Superconduct&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Everything except scrap products&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: center&#34;&gt;⭐⭐⭐&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Gleba&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/bioflux.png&#34; alt=&#34;bioflux&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Bioflux&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;, &lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/biter_egg.png&#34; alt=&#34;biter_egg&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Biter egg&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;, Agricultural science&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Fuel, &lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/chemical_plant.png&#34; alt=&#34;chemical_plant&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Chemical&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;s, defense supplies&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: center&#34;&gt;⭐⭐⭐&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Aquilo&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/cryogenic_plant.png&#34; alt=&#34;cryogenic_plant&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Cryogenic&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;, &lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/fusion_reactor.png&#34; alt=&#34;fusion_reactor&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Fusion&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;/&lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/fusion_generator.png&#34; alt=&#34;fusion_generator&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Fusion&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;, Ice platform items&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Everything except ice/water products&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: center&#34;&gt;⭐⭐&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Space Platform&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;Nothing direct (platform stays in orbit)&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: left&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;game-slot&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1319/images/icon/rocket_silo.png&#34; alt=&#34;rocket_silo&#34; class=&#34;game-img&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;span class=&#34;game-name&#34;&gt;Rocket silo&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA; parts, science packs&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td style=&#34;text-align: center&#34;&gt;⭐⭐&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/tbody&gt;&#xA;&lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;cargo-rocket-automation&#34;&gt;Cargo Rocket Automation&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Automating rocket launches requires three elements:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
